# --- Jupyter ---
**/.ipynb_checkpoints/

# NOTE: airsight/backend/app/data_processed/ is intentionally NOT ignored.
# The generated artifacts (meta.json, stations.json, *.csv.gz, bogota.geojson)
# are committed so deploys work without re-running the ETL. hourly.csv.gz is the
# largest (~3.5 MB) but well under GitHub limits, so we track it too — this lets
# the Docker build skip the ETL entirely and start fast on free tiers.
